Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 0

# Run everything hidden: clear screen, set empty prompt, launch script
Hide
Type "export PS1='' && clear && ./demo-script.sh"
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
Show
Sleep 23s
